imdb.plot outline: Each week, Doc Mock has digs deep into his movie mausoleum archives to unearth a film that hasn't been viewed by willing mortal eyes in decades. Joined by his assistant nurse, Miss Diagnosis, and his control booth operator, a mutant eyeball named "Licky", Doc Mock exposes audiences and a special guest comedian to these bizarre b-movies from yesteryear while providing live, improvised commentary.
imdb.title: Doc Mock's Movie Mausoleum
